{"tid":1249164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果屋企人有習慣睇cctvb既入一入黎。","createTime":"2019-06-21T15:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T16:59:08.000Z","uid":211066,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d248cac5a8c7a39c6b42ebabd561133a96ddbb90","tid":1249164,"uid":211066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"講多無謂，CCTVB新聞部有幾狗大家都知。<br />\n<br />\n我係到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲各位</span></span>，返到屋企休息既同時唔好唔記得，要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">解釋！解釋！解釋！</span>下比你屋企人聽，佢地睇到既，同你係現場睇到既有嘜野分別。<br />\n<br />\n因為你既解釋，絕對會影響老一輩既人點睇呢場運動。而老一輩既人，唔洗諗呀，8成都係睇CCTVB既新聞台去了解現場情況。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩我見到老媽子睇緊電視，佢眼神開始對班狗出現同理心，就係因為CCTVB不斷播一啲受影響市民既回應，又播示威者拆欄杆既畫面。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，你可以做既就係解釋多次，點解呢班示威者要咁做，我地既目的係嘜野，政府無做嘜野，班狗做過啲嘜野等等。<br />\n<br />\n我好怕呢場戰爭過多一兩個月就會失去一班原本支持我地既人。<br />\n<br />\n我好愛呢個香港，所以我有責任提醒身邊既所有人，每一個香港人都有責任守護屬於佢地既香港！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加油！</span>"},{"pid":"5a492f185d8624e0321a1652831f9f18b5a4e12a","tid":1249164,"uid":211066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好睇小自己可以出到既每一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762a8eda57ce34f6b24bd2bd40e8b373211e4b21","tid":1249164,"uid":18639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"直接CUT左佢啦"},{"pid":"1b655bb881f89ed314d87d4f1fa8539e8d97e1db","tid":1249164,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029319383d3bcfc1b3cc61d86d7c51c8ff244331","tid":1249164,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"忍唔住 我會搬走"},{"pid":"4a721b483d0c273aec618a20926c31da6e8d52a3","tid":1249164,"uid":211066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"762a8eda57ce34f6b24bd2bd40e8b373211e4b21","tid":1249164,"uid":18639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"直接CUT左佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"我係一個有品德既人，我係唔會咁對自己老母，最多話佢兩句...你咁樣只係剝奪佢睇電視既自由，你試下解釋下先。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9f77d5dbb8599d9dff1451711844fad7acaeea","tid":1249164,"uid":86643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"頭先一路開住港台32直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n播交通消息就轉31<br />\n再唔係就VIU或者香港開電視啦"},{"pid":"171b209c3c2068a74d9fd7aeaa36ab6fe1aa882c","tid":1249164,"uid":211066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9f77d5dbb8599d9dff1451711844fad7acaeea","tid":1249164,"uid":86643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"頭先一路開住港台32直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n播交通消息就轉31<br />\n再唔係就VIU或者香港開電視啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"如果大家熟茶餐廳老闆既話都叫佢地唔好再播濕鳩tvb，好多打工既都係食住lunch睇架。<br />\n<br />\n大家千奇唔好怕醜，講一句可能可以改變好多野，佢地都係選民黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場仗，贏得一票得一票。"},{"pid":"033c16cc1b39937f8798ee42b13dc4aaafa24bf1","tid":1249164,"uid":211066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"各位，我地呢鋪真係要用盡一切辦法令香港人團結起黎。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要年青人企出黎，我地要哂所有香港人呀。係所有！"},{"pid":"988000d9771f1eead9ed436a069c27e5bf